videos.name: RAGBRAI XLIII Logo  Revealed
videos.shortDescription: We are excited to reveal our new logo for RAGBRAI XLIII and 2015! If you join us on our ride across the state next year, youll be sure to see welcoming Iowans, lots of farmland and well youll just have to watch the video to find out.
videos.longDescription: We are excited to reveal our new logo for RAGBRAI XLIII and 2015! If you join us on our ride across the state next year, youll be sure to see welcoming Iowans, lots of farmland and well youll just have to watch the video to find out. And be sure to take a close look at the logo, as there are a few hidden surprises. Love the new logo? Head over to RAGBRAI.com/shop and check out our brand new RAGBRAI XLIII merchandise including comfy sweatshirts, long sleeved shirts, and t-shirts for both men and women. And dont forget  RAGBRAI XLIII registration opens November 15th at RAGBRAI.com/Registration.

videos.name: $1,500 for a bicyclist's life
videos.shortDescription: Bicyclist Shawn Gosch of Onawa was hit and killed June 20, 2014, by a motorist on Iowa Highway 7 west of Manson. Under Iowa law, the driver of the vehicle was charged with a misdemeanor for unsafe passing and fined little more than $1,550.
